welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Renaico, the charming city known for its rich cultural heritage and breathtaking natural beauty. We invite you to immerse yourself in our vibrant community and explore all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The largest terminal at Los Angeles Airport, serving major airlines such as American Airlines, Delta, and United.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Los Angeles Airport, serving international airlines such as Air Canada, Air China, and Avianca.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: A mid-sized terminal at Los Angeles Airport, serving airlines such as JetBlue, Spirit, and Virgin America.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport, but may require a login and have limited speeds.
